org.openimaj.text.nlp.textpipe.annotations

Class TextPipeAnnotation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.text.nlp.textpipe.annotations.TextPipeAnnotation
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    NamedEntityAnnotation, PhraseAnnotation, POSAnnotation, RawTextAnnotation, TokenAnnotation

    public abstract class TextPipeAnnotation
extends Object
    Classes that extend TextPipeAnnotation are annotations and annotatable. Annotations are a HashMap keyed on the class of the annotation, adding a new annotation T extends TextPipeAnnotation will be added to the the list of Annotations of that class already added.
    Author:
    Laurence Willmore (lgw1e10@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
